香港咁多劏房都無事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:11:59.000Z","msg":"證明肺炎在香港已變成廢炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d64df43deef50c9b5149742e402b4ccb71d2c4","tid":1990511,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:12:29.000Z","msg":"陳雲: Just a flu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c1e03b85bfd3a8190ca188c2b1da9d684084f5","tid":1990511,"uid":49977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:12:52.000Z","msg":"吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a725c81e5b6767032d8e0533b01cebae59e2f563","tid":1990511,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"唔爆又搞到我失業<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"bbe07c1cc79b1f1fd8831d057716ac15a9f0ed8c","tid":1990511,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb0de2b9f96a595975051f84ac9395b00040379","tid":1990511,"uid":130742,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:57:38.000Z","msg":"出街市民表示：零確診驚閪咩，社區大爆發先算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:13:43.000Z","msg":"禁止返工先講"},{"pid":"3f10e3b3191c422cabd8535c9b3bcef8ec1e0aa3","tid":1990511,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07c2374540e810c93f9713b78948aa66984fdc4b","tid":1990511,"uid":16164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要經濟攬炒必定要武肺持續"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:15:51.000Z","msg":"陳茂波話反修例及疫情都唔能夠攬炒經濟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反修例及疫情雙重打擊 陳茂波稱未見大規模資金流走<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200426/bkn-20200426105634902-0426_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200426%2Fbkn-20200426105634902-0426_00822_001.html&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4KooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=b11c6d08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200426/bkn-20200426105634902-0426_00822_001.html</a><br />\n&quot;雖然社會事件及暴力衝擊曾損害市場信心，新冠肺炎疫情亦令港股一度顯著隨外圍受壓，但同樣<span style=\"color: red;\">未見大規模的資金流走</span>。他指，近期港匯持續偏強，徘徊在強方兌換保證水平，甚至多次觸及上限，反映<span style=\"color: red;\">有資金流入</span>。&quot;<br />\n&quot;即使目前樓價仍處市場較難負擔的高水平，但<span style=\"color: red;\">住宅物業市場出現斷崖式下跌的風險不大</span>。他認為，儘管疫情對全球以至香港經濟及金融巿場構成壓力，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港金融風險仍屬可控水平</span>。&quot;"},{"pid":"471243dba0d4f769917dfbd0e37ede9e6b0558c8","tid":1990511,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實全世界都開始係 美國佬去沙灘玩"},{"pid":"9dae567141e2495961d26b120cad357ad5568a09","tid":1990511,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"471243dba0d4f769917dfbd0e37ede9e6b0558c8","tid":1990511,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實全世界都開始係 美國佬去沙灘玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:23:01.000Z","msg":"沙灘空氣流通，感染風險極微，驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee566079d193a7d0e54a8265161ff31d2870b62f","tid":1990511,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:24:13.000Z","msg":"又話勁過沙士10倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b979d0e8948a59c8c29688a927601cc25d06e10","tid":1990511,"uid":16164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f10e3b3191c422cabd8535c9b3bcef8ec1e0aa3","tid":1990511,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07c2374540e810c93f9713b78948aa66984fdc4b","tid":1990511,"uid":16164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要經濟攬炒必定要武肺持續"},"citedBy":1,"re